.000Z","msg":"呢排身邊好多人都話個心痛痛地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced4fef684e78761ced67f52b5c9896d12b4d28f","tid":1066032,"uid":143598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a14f86edd6e0f1ccf5557ab01986dc8b98fc98b","tid":1066032,"uid":121412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T16:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XdV7R5p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXdV7R5p.png&h=553b3aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係過高一係過低<br />\n有時心口會有抽住抽住痛<br />\n呼吸困難，上左瑪麗檢查心電圖<br />\nx光/同抽血，佢話冇事。但係又冇講點解咁樣<br />\n<br />\n好怕訓訓下死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T00:46:33.000Z","msg":"做運動心電圖"},{"pid":"5c57bfc0e41ed49f1d8e7c66269dcdf707d31ba5","tid":1066032,"uid":119008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1098e95dee0b61961c96f531c7ef2b39ece9303a","tid":1066032,"uid":121412,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5e1038b23ec9964eb64e1f5d4d26c32ac40f616e","tid":1066032,"uid":81283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T17:07:35.000Z","msg":"有冇訓唔足教，夜訓"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T23:09:53.000Z","msg":"經常夜訓 訓好少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T00:48:09.000Z","msg":"會心悸 通頂得多身體休息唔夠真係會咁<br />\n真係因住有日搞到猝死<br />\n唔係講笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前都試過咁<br />\n跟手果日暈左"},{"pid":"27d225fdf89bfa8ea9a66d4ae4d102a357fbbb7d","tid":1066032,"uid":192303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a14f86edd6e0f1ccf5557ab01986dc8b98fc98b","tid":1066032,"uid":121412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T16:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XdV7R5p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXdV7R5p.png&h=553b3aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係過高一係過低<br />\n有時心口會有抽住抽住痛<br />\n呼吸困難，上左瑪麗檢查心電圖<br />\nx光/同抽血，佢話冇事。但係又冇講點解咁樣<br />\n<br />\n好怕訓訓下死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T01:25:29.000Z","msg":"做holter/loop recorder"},{"pid":"1fe70552db671114ddef1ae51ff6e93314f782af","tid":1066032,"uid":192303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"229985d6b383b0b9e5d784df3e1cb0e389bc87b4","tid":1066032,"uid":121412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6311a4ec3d3306de691c995c09e1eca1e1863ea","tid":1066032,"uid":188470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:49:36.000Z","msg":"樓主點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:15:09.000Z","msg":"入左醫院，今晚留院觀察"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T01:26:26.000Z","msg":"私家？"},{"pid":"284818e92d3f8c3292bddde3211ee10eb4147df8","tid":1066032,"uid":192303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d54d394244b9ccd776c65a7dd3284d4d2c316529","tid":1066032,"uid":14678,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a42c7720c7c7d2e603650db1925f788878150dda","tid":1066032,"uid":121412,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T13:37:24.000Z","msg":"不過我想係度講<br />\nApple watch真係好撚垃圾<br />\n<br />\n我宜家長期貼左部心跳機<br />\n<br />\nApple有時顯示47，但醫院部心跳機冇試過咁低<br />\n<br />\n問過醫生，醫院話如果早博apple watch係會二下當左一下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:01:19.000Z","msg":"印象中Apple Watch係有太約5%誤差<br />\n同埋有時係會有wrong detection<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但個人認為絕大部分時間都準 （我試過對住心跳機對個數都係得1-2bpm誤差）<br />\n你個Case 132其實唔算高<br />\n我試過跳到210<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過你低到37就要注意下<br />\n<br />\n利申準備排期做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T01:28:27.000Z","msg":"我都試過210<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過又係睇醫生捉唔到係咩嚟<br />\n依家戒曬咖啡 茶 酒，依家跳少咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8fdc7451c66ed2ebd13452dc1735b5eb3dc3a0","tid":1066032,"uid":13396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T01:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都成日係咁，但無理到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7d8005e515ebed39f4e1addc3ed4226916215f","tid":1066032,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T01:41:20.000Z","msg":"如果冇事就攞吓假放鬆吓啦ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好到時出事令屋企人擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76720a6bf7203889308ff2108c5c3f2e982a05b","tid":1066032,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T01:50:58.000Z","msg":"樓主如果無事記得上返嚟報平安，唔使等其他巴絲擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764b240b971e8c16c28657d8a7dbc7147799e695","tid":1066032,"uid":121412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d76720a6bf7203889308ff2108c5c3f2e982a05b","tid":1066032,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T01:50:58.000Z","msg":"樓主如果無事記得上返嚟報平安，唔使等其他巴絲擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:16:42.000Z","msg":"一陣見埋心臟科醫生先知，<br />\n<br />\n多謝咁多位巴打 關心。詳情今晚報告"},{"pid":"5b4d62396f903c0224065eb62ee4f7f798a39b64","tid":1066032,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T08:20:00.000Z","msg":"sick sinus syndrome<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9a2f7df1a1238b957c83738664b2e2f85a1a9f","tid":1066032,"uid":121412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:28:53.000Z","msg":"出左院，話我血壓高 壓力大<br />\n有早博，抽左我幾次血去驗<br />\n<br />\n仲要驗24小時尿，排期做動態心電圖同超聲波"},{"pid":"15dd0ac1670fe1e350a8feb331690621bea6e577","tid":1066032,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:51:37.000Z","msg":"排到病發都未到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8173643486fb007aa2dc503b0b57eb5b6e82f7fc","tid":1066032,"uid":73660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:53:47.000Z","msg":"前排都試過個心有d拿住拿住 ，跟住頭暈左成3個星期，血壓keep住高，心跳keep住90至100，入院check左咩都無左 再過多個月血壓正常返 下壓都係偏高，樓主可能係膽固醇高 甚至有血管塞塞地"},{"pid":"ccc02f44fa6718073316890e387531b3cc87a22e","tid":1066032,"uid":121412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15dd0ac1670fe1e350a8feb331690621bea6e577","tid":1066032,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:51:37.000Z","msg":"排到病發都未到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T10:00:16.000Z","msg":"所以聽日去私家租機做動態心電圖"},{"pid":"1fccfdcdfb933369095ad7181c4f376a3ab0ef7b","tid":1066032,"uid":121412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8173643486fb007aa2dc503b0b57eb5b6e82f7fc","tid":1066032,"uid":73660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:53:47.000Z","msg":"前排都試過個心有d拿住拿住 ，跟住頭暈左成3個星期，血壓keep住高，心跳keep住90至100，入院check左咩都無左 再過多個月血壓正常返 下壓都係偏高，樓主可能係膽固醇高 甚至有血管塞塞地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T10:00:46.000Z","msg":"我都唔知<br />\n香港地窮既話就真係等死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9474737fe1d2f3b6931bb1118024589c8981f911","tid":1066032,"uid":25538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T12:50:45.000Z","msg":"你點同醫生講？"},{"pid":"270327eb98037e40236f5a47f4d929afc7ff5556","tid":1066032,"uid":158166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:44:06.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪睇急症然後收你入院？"},{"pid":"fe0bb231db5ca6451e749fd66eaeb666499758db","tid":1066032,"uid":207482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T00:28:56.000Z","msg":"你血液含氧正唔正常？<br />\n之前係ICU做 見最多人有急性呼吸困難同心口痛 係因為爆肺/ 肺動脈栓塞/ 心肌梗塞 所以記得睇埋個肺"},{"pid":"5af36632de1d46f8f289